A Rarity - 11 Yearold OFC Cutan

Whisky

This year, the firm of Schenley celebrates its 25th Anniversary. To commemorate the event, they have put in bottle the small remaining quantity of their remarkable Eleven Year Old O.F.C. Canadian Whiskey.

The number of bottles of such aged whiskey, of course, is small indeed and surely it will be gone before Christmas. Rarely, have we experienced a Canadian whiskey of such light delicacy, harmony, smoothness and fine bouquet. It will surely delight the lover of fine old spirits.

The handsome commemorative bottle is beautifully packaged in an impressive gold velour bag—an ex- ceptional item to acquire now (while still available) to give to your friends during this coming Christmas.
